predictions.article: USDA Prepares to Protect Farmers in a Trade War
predictions.prediction: The implementation of the Market Facilitation Program (MFP) will lead to direct payments to U.S. farmers within the next month to mitigate the impact of retaliatory tariffs.

predictions.article: U.S. agriculture is in crosshairs of China's tariff retaliation
predictions.prediction: China's countermeasures will result in a 10% increase in soymeal and rapeseed meal futures on the Dalian Commodities Exchange within two weeks.
